Paper: hep-th/9612010

Date: 1996-12-01

Title: Weight Systems from Feynman Diagrams

Comments: 25 pages, latex, uses epsf, references updated, to appear in J.Knot

Th.RamJournal-ref: J.Knot Theor.Ramifications 7 (1998) 61-85

We find that the overall UV divergences of a renormalizable field theory withtrivalent vertices fulfil a four-term relation. They thus come close toestablish a weight system. This provides a first explanation of the recentsuccessful association of renormalization theory with knot theory.